thread.title: Laura in Poway
thread.title_full: San Diego Self Storage reviewed by Laura in Poway

author: Laura in Poway
title: Laura in Poway
text: I have used this storage company twice now and will keep coming back whenever I need a storage unit. They have always been clean, fair, and have great prices and move-in specials. Plus, the price is locked for a year, but leases are month-to-month.
